&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;If you are passionate about hands-on engineering, systems thinking, and delivering best-in-class solutions, join us. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Think beyond conventional boundaries, embrace technical challenges, and be part of a team that turns &lt;strong&gt;visionary concepts into reality&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
