&lt;p&gt;If you thrive in ambiguity, build before you&#39;re told to, move fast across functions, and believe that a clean insight delivered fast beats a perfect deck delivered late — read on.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Actually Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
