&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;11,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;11,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Lead Creative Production:&lt;/strong&gt; Step behind the camera as the leading creative voice on photo and video shoots. Partner with directors, photographers, and production teams to ensure final assets match the original strategic intent.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;11,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;11,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Champion an AI-Native Workflow:&lt;/strong&gt; Actively integrate Figma, AI generation tools, and emerging platforms into your daily concepting and layout phases to explore a broader range of visual directions at lightning speed.&lt;/p&gt;
